9.1. Governing Law and Jurisdiction: This License shall be governed by the substantive laws of Switzerland. Any dispute shall be resolved by arbitration under the WIPO Arbitration Rules, with the seat of arbitration in Geneva, Switzerland, in English, before a sole arbitrator.
9.2. Severability: If any provision of this License is held unenforceable, it shall be changed to accomplish the objectives of such provision to the greatest extent possible, and the remaining provisions will continue in full force and effect.
9.3. Entire Agreement: This License constitutes the entire agreement between the parties with respect to the subject matter hereof.
